    "Specifically, the sensitivity and specificity of the model increased as the temporal window size increased.",
    "However, as illustrated in Fig. 3, the specificity is low and therefore resulting in a false positive rate per hour (FP/h) that is still too high for practical usage.",
    "The LOOCV method was then applied for validating subject-specific models on the PEDESITE dataset.",
    "We followed the same training procedures as reported for the CHB-MIT dataset.",
    "Table 3 presents the results of varying the temporal window size."
